5:
Wow, this is tasty! Great
recommendation Stella, the red
bean and mochi are delicious!
13:
I'm glad you managed to get some
time off, Levy. You were busy right
from the beginning of the year,
weren't you?
18:
Yes, but I got to have a one-on-one
interview with Trista, and that was...
relaxing...
23:
H-hey, there's no need to worry
about getting mobbed by fans out
in Yamato. Let's just enjoy some
time off and not worry about work!
28:
Y-yeah! It's important to kick back
sometimes and—
32:
Come on, it'll be fine! You promised
we'd go find the shrine together!
38: Hello. Is everything all right, you two?
44:
...A shrine that only appears around
New Year's and grants any wish
made, huh?
48:
We can't let kids go off on their own
like that. The yokai present too great
a threat.
54:
This looks like it'll be fun. I didn't think
I'd get the chance to go on an
adventure today.
59: You really do love adventuring, huh.
63:
Don't worry. No matter what
happens...
67: Stay behind us! We can handle this—
79: Heh, wow! Yokai aren't scary at all!
82: You can always count on Stella.
95: ...All right. I hate to do this!
102:
Yes. The children and yokai are all
fine.
111: It's all right now, right Stella?
122:
They're saying they want to be your
friends.
125:
If you think so too, why not give it a
shot?
129:
...But you never know when danger
might reveal itself again.
132:
Don't forget that the most important
rule of adventuring is getting home
safe. You can go home now if you
want.
135:
I wanna keep going! There's
something I want to say, after all!
137: ...All right, then. We'll keep you safe.
141:
Is that the wish-granting shrine you
two were talking about?
147:
...Gimme lots of money so things get
easier for mom!
149:
...Hmph. So much for that. What was
the point in coming here?
152:
...It's frustrating to take risks and
worked hard but still don't end up
with what you want, isn't it?
155:
But you don't really think it was
pointless coming here, do you? You
achieved something special, right?
158:
I'm not telling you to give up on
what you want the most.
160:
Focusing on what matters to you
while also being thankful for what
you do have...
164: I think that's what's really important.
167:
...I'm happy I got to make new
friends. I want to be even better
friends with the yokai!
173:
Wow! Maybe my wish will get
granted after all!
175:
Thank you, Levy. I'm so glad I came
here!
178:
I'm also glad I got to adventure with
you!
180:
But remember, adventuring is
dangerous. Make sure you talk to us
or another adult next time you want
to go somewhere, okay?
186: That's what I like to hear!
189:
Now then, I think it's time for us to go
on an adventure back home!
193:
Hey, Levy? I think you deserve all the
praise your fans give you.
197:
You can count on me to save you
from a tight spot, make the most of
an adventure, and look really cool
while doing it, too.
201:
I'm the one and only Levy Gracia,
after all!
